也取得了两连胜。 同时宋凯也确实在搞青训，虽然搞青训这个事情不是一天两天能见成果，但是宋凯确实是做了很多青训的功课，他真不是把搞青训挂在嘴边，他是尽力做事了。 那么说句不好听，大家都骂中国足协，可是中国足球想要变好，这也离不开中国足协的出力，那么宋凯在足协也干 1 年时间了，他干的究竟怎么样，还算可以吗"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-6cf98e800da47ec27add337e06c8ea63_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "40 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/4338540415"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIofLozIub8MknEAMaCTExMTg0NDMxNSCrlOK5BjAAOD1AG3IKNDMzODU0MDQxNXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "28_1732011960.736178", "card_id": "Q_3698001218", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 35}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "在工作中，面对总是「抢功」的同事和「甩锅」的领导，怎样巧妙应对才不影响人际关系？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "在工作场景里，常常会有同事把本应属于大家或者是你的功劳据为己有，也会有领导把一些得罪人的话让你说。这种情况很棘手，因为处理不好可能会引发同事间的矛盾，影响职场人际关系。但如果不处理，自己又会很委屈。所以想知道有什么巧妙的方法，既能拿回属于自己的成果或者保护自己应得的利益，又能维持良好的工作关系呢？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-f64be61ff6d01ef5fb96322020f60e83_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "40 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/3698001218"}}, "attached_info": "CkEIofLozIub8MknEAMaCTExMTcxNjM2MCCvt765BjAAOIsBQBxyCjM2OTgwMDEyMTh4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "29_1732011960.736501", "card_id": "Q_4495394152", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 161}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待老师将日常教学中涉及未成年人的视频发到网上的行为？记录生活的短视频分享应把握哪些原则和边界？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "近日，有一位老师因在短视频平台上发布一条「给上课爱说话的学生戴小蜜蜂」的视频而走红。视频里，一位学生因上课爱说话而被戴上老师的「小蜜蜂」扩音器。 该视频引起热议并被广泛转发，随后，不少网友都纷纷晒出自己给班上学生戴「小蜜蜂」的视频，并表示这种方法很有效。 图源：当事人社交账号 11 月 17 日，这位老师在个人社交账号上发声称自己已经迫于压力选择离职。 「在发布那条视频的时候我没有任何恶意，只是单纯地想分享一下治理课堂秩序的好方法，该学生家长也在我的视频底下点赞评论，并认可了我的方法。」 「但是由于视频的播放量越来越高，学生家长害怕对孩子产生影响，于是我第一时间下架了视频，并对学生和家长表达了歉意。第二天孩子来学校以后，我也是在积极观察着孩子的状态，好在孩子上课很积极，课间和朋友们相处也算融洽。」给学生戴「小蜜蜂」的女老师道歉：已离职 - 川观新闻"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-23429020c52e3a843e3023710fe7dcff_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "40 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/4495394152"}}, "attached_info": "CkEIofLozIub8MknEAMaCTExMTg3NTgwNyDJjOy5BjAAOOoCQB1yCjQ0OTUzOTQxNTJ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}], "paging": {"is_end": true, "is_start": false, "next": "", "previous": "", "totals": 0}, "fresh_text": "热榜已更新", "display_num": 15, "display_first": true, "fb_bill_main_rise": 0, "head_zone": {"type": "billboard_lantern", "data": [{"id": "1842207634020786178", "link_url": "https://www.zhihu.com/parker/campaign/1842165000535429120", "title": "「2024 知乎科学盛典」明日上线节目单揭晓", "source_type": 0, "attached_info": "Ci4QABoTMTg0MjIwNzYzNDAyMDc4NjE3OHITMTg0MjIwNzYzNDAyMDc4NjE3OHgA", "tag": "关注", "tag_bg_color": "GYL01A"}, {"id": "1724871100431802368", "link_url": "https://www.zhihu.com/appview/community_construction", "title": "辟谣专区", "source_type": 0, "attached_info": "Ci4QABoTMTcyNDg3MTEwMDQzMTgwMjM2OHITMTcyNDg3MTEwMDQzMTgwMjM2OHgA", "tag": "辟谣", "tag_bg_color": "GRD01A"}]}, "head_zones": [{"type": "billboard_lantern", "data": [{"id": "1842207634020786178", "link_url": "https://www.zhihu.com/parker/campaign/1842165000535429120", "title": "「2024 知乎科学盛典」明日上线节目单揭晓", "source_type": 0, "attached_info": "Ci4QABoTMTg0MjIwNzYzNDAyMDc4NjE3OHITMTg0MjIwNzYzNDAyMDc4NjE3OHgA", "tag": "关注", "tag_bg_color": "GYL01A"}, {"id": "1724871100431802368", "link_url": "https://www.zhihu.com/appview/community_construction", "title": "辟谣专区", "source_type": 0, "attached_info": "Ci4QABoTMTcyNDg3MTEwMDQzMTgwMjM2OHITMTcyNDg3MTEwMDQzMTgwMjM2OHgA", "tag": "辟谣", "tag_bg_color": "GRD01A"}]}]}